     C           WND2      IFNE 0
     C                     ADD  1         WND1
     C                     END
      *
     C*------------------*
     C*  ...１日分...  *
     C*------------------*
     C           WND1      DIV  WSYOS     WND3    70
     C                     MVR            WND4    70
     C           WND4      IFNE 0
     C                     ADD  1         WND3
     C                     END
      *
     C*----------------------*
     C*  ...０．５日分...  *
