     C*                    ...ﾅ ﾎﾞ ﾓ - k ]...                        *
     C*  ...Ｎ　Ｎ＋１　Ｎ＋２月　旬単位　日当箱数・内示数計算...  *
     C*--------------------------------------------------------------*
     C           SUBMET    BEGSR
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         HN1
     C                     Z-ADD0         HN2
     C                     Z-ADD0         HN3
      *
     C                     Z-ADD1         A
     C           1         DO   3         A
     C                     Z-ADD0         WTS1
     C                     Z-ADD0         WNS1
     C                     Z-ADD0         WTS2
     C                     Z-ADD0         WNS2
     C                     Z-ADD0         WTS3
     C                     Z-ADD0         WNS3
